'', ''周边配套'', ''整体满意度'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232g12000as0v6bzE047_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0233512000as0zx8n4D3C_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236g12000as0y73k0D6E_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232812000as11t4cCF21_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230z12000as0rf1v08F6_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231912000as0yabt6F27_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236z12000as0wxye70D5_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '每次出差必选的酒店，服务特别好，这次早上就到了酒店前台找到有空房直接给提前入住了', '每次出差必选的酒店，服务特别好，这次早上就到了酒店前台找到有空房直接给提前入住了，特别感谢酒店的人性化服务', '2023-02-21', 5, '[''前台服务'', ''整体满意度'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232012000ap63es1AA00_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '美食加美景，不愧是广州老牌的五星酒店，软件服务比硬件更胜一筹，下回有机会一定再次', '美食加美景，不愧是广州老牌的五星酒店，软件服务比硬件更胜一筹，下回有机会一定再次入住，五星好评!', '2023-03-02', 5, '[''整体满意度'', ''餐饮设施'', ''景观/朝向'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231m12000aqai6m9C4BD_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234a12000aqahy4b5075_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231l12000aqahrow74E1_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235512000aqajqo61FC1_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0233w12000aqai8nq6DC0_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231n12000aqajtq61390_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '很高兴这次来广州选择了花园酒店～ 很有历史沉淀感的酒店，后花园非常漂亮，名副其实', '很高兴这次来广州选择了花园酒店～ 很有历史沉淀感的酒店，后花园非常漂亮，名副其实的花园酒店，Billy替我们办理了原房续住省去了我们换房间的麻烦，特别感恩感谢～ 感受到了广州人民的友好与好客，会推荐以后来广州的朋友入住此酒店～', '2023-09-09', 5, '[''整体满意度'', ''前台服务'', ''公共设施'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0233l12000c3iyezfF0A1_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230e12000c3j09kaAAE0_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232712000c3izrfw562D_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '推荐推荐，还是很好的，赞????，比较适合商旅客人入住的酒店，短暂的体验岭南文化', '推荐推荐，还是很好的，赞????，比较适合商旅客人入住的酒店，短暂的体验岭南文化，酒店设计的文化植入点恰到好处', '2023-02-21', 5, '[''整体满意度'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236e12000ap4kxxn03DE_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230v12000ap4p0ki981D_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232c12000ap4m4vrCCFF_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231s12000ap4mnqy26EF_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0237012000ap4hnwo0D76_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236012000ap4ldhq711A_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236n12000ap4ojln55D1_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230r12000ap4idq8E96C_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '来过几次了，这个价钱有个套房就真的很值，而且前台小姐姐超有礼貌。不过停车不太方便', '来过几次了，这个价钱有个套房就真的很值，而且前台小姐姐超有礼貌。不过停车不太方便，没有独立化妆台和全身镜，可以改进', '2023-02-12', 5, '[''性价比'', ''前台服务'', ''房间设施'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234i12000anqik7tD5BC_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236312000anqinpg2FF1_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235s12000anqijm90F92_R_150_150_R5_Q70_